[[Habeen]] researchers used [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] '''''Notz''''' at the [[Battle of Mylok IV|Mylok IV Conflict]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Corvette ''Notz'' docked with Habeen containers, rescuing critical [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] technology from an attack by [[Nharwaak]] dissidents. ''Notz'' was an old corvette, and it suffered a heavy beating from the Nharwaak attackers.

